  "texts": [
    "The recurrent transformer based on τ is as follows, where the comma between two sequences concatenates them:",
    "In the above, h i and y i are respectively the hidden state and output of the recurrent transformer at position i.",
    "Equation 5 initializes the recurrence at position 1, Equation 6 iteratively applies the transformer function with causal attention between position i+ 1 and position i, and Equation 7 closes the recurrence at the last position.",
    "The trainable accumulation parameter α serves to accumulate a weighted portion of the hidden state h i-1 into the working states of the network.",
    "Intuitively, α = 1 favors memorization, while α = 0 favors generalization."
  ],
